params.prompt: A upper-body photo of a single {{step1.output.gender}} img 18-year-old teenager in 90s style, wearing a natural-looking 90s high school uniform. The image should resemble a 90s yearbook photo with a natural, relaxed posture, showing the entire body, including hands. Use a deep, rich blue background with a seamless, cloudy, mist-like texture. The texture should feature a soft, cloudy gradient effect with various shades of blue, ranging from light to dark, creating a smooth, mottled appearance. The entire surface should have a subtle, cloudy pattern without distinct shapes or edges, providing a calm and consistent backdrop
